  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nFrom validator log:\r\n```\r\nAug-12 10:07:40.012 []                error: Error on attestations routine slot=6037, committeeIndex=0 message=Error producing attestation - Timeout request\r\nError: Error producing attestation - Timeout request\r\n    at HttpClient.request (/usr/app/node_modules/@chainsafe/lodestar-api/lib/client/utils/httpClient.js:60:27)\r\n    at runMicrotasks (<anonymous>)\r\n    at processTicksAndRejections (internal/process/task_queues.js:95:5)\r\n    at runNextTicks (internal/process/task_queues.js:64:3)\r\n    at listOnTimeout (internal/timers.js:526:9)\r\n    at processTimers (internal/timers.js:500:7)\r\n    at HttpClient.json (/usr/app/node_modules/@chainsafe/lodestar-api/lib/client/utils/httpClient.js:28:16)\r\n    at Object.request [as produceAttestationData] (/usr/app/node_modules/@chainsafe/lodestar-api/lib/client/utils/client.js:43:25)\r\n    at AttestationService.produceAndPublishAttestations (/usr/app/node_modules/@chainsafe/lodestar-validator/lib/services/attestation.js:61:32)\r\n    at AttestationService.publishAttestationsAndAggregates (/usr/app/node_modules/@chainsafe/lodestar-validator/lib/services/attestation.js:40:29)\r\n```\r\nOur node shows that it may takes up to 8s to produce attestations\r\n<img width=\"841\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-08-12 at 17 12 11\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/129179851-5560c3f8-cb8f-4d93-89a2-6fa0c4924efc.png\">\r\n\r\nIt looks like our node is very busy.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nNo error",
